<td style="width:0%;padding:0px 0px 0px 2px;" rowspan="5"><a href="/wiki/File:Ratzinger_Szczepanow_Derivative.png" class="image" title="Ratzinger Szczepanow Derivative.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f0/Ratzinger_Szczepanow_Derivative.png/100px-Ratzinger_Szczepanow_Derivative.png" width="100" height="103" border="0" /></a></td>
